trans-unit.source: Imports standard transport binding elements from [Web Services Description Language](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=96160) (WSDL) documents with attached policy expressions.
trans-unit.target: 표준 전송 바인딩 요소를 가져오는 [웹 서비스 기술 언어](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=96160) 연결 된 정책 식 문서 (WSDL).

trans-unit.source: The `TransportBindingElementImporter` type is an implementation of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyImportExtension> interfaces.
trans-unit.target: `TransportBindingElementImporter` 종류는의 구현에서 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension>및 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyImportExtension>인터페이스.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyImportExtension> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension>

trans-unit.source: It imports the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpsTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerTransportBindingElement> instances from WSDL service metadata.
trans-unit.target: 가져온는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpsTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement>, 및 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerTransportBindingElement>인스턴스 WSDL에서 서비스 메타 데이터입니다.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerTransportBindingElement> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MsmqTransportBindingElement> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TcpTransportBindingElement> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpsTransportBindingElement> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: When these <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement> types are imported, the `TransportBindingElementImporter` type also imports the addressing information from the WSDL metadata.
trans-unit.target: 때 이러한 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>형식을 가져올는 `TransportBindingElementImporter` 형식 또한 WSDL 메타 데이터에서 주소 지정 정보를 가져옵니다.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElementImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElementImporter"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: Imports a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement> instance from the policy attached to the WSDL binding.
trans-unit.target: 가져오기는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>인스턴스는 정책에서 WSDL 바인딩에 연결 된.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: Adds custom policy assertions to the WSDL bindings in WSDL documents that are to be imported.
trans-unit.target: 가져올 WSDL 문서의 WSDL 바인딩에 사용자 지정 정책 어설션을 추가 합니다.

trans-unit.source: This method attaches a policy expression to WSDL bindings that already have attached policies.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드는 이미 정책이 연결 되어 있는 WSDL 바인딩에 정책 식을 연결 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The added policy expression contains a custom policy assertion that contains the SOAP transport URI from the SOAP binding.
trans-unit.target: 추가 된 정책 식은 SOAP 바인딩의 SOAP 전송 URI를 포함 하는 사용자 지정 정책 어설션을 포함 합니다.

trans-unit.source: This policy assertion is used when importing the endpoint to import the correct transport binding element.
trans-unit.target: 이 정책 어설션은 올바른 전송 바인딩 요소를 가져올 끝점을 가져올 때 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The collection of WSDL documents that are to be imported.

trans-unit.source: The collection of policy assertions that are to be imported.
